&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Regulatory Framework&lt;/strong&gt;: Allegations involve violations of SEBI Act, LODR Regulations, and PFUTP Regulations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Noticees&lt;/strong&gt;: Key parties include Noticees 1, 2, 3, 6, 7, and 8.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Transactions&lt;/strong&gt;: Loans between entities were scrutinized for classification as related party transactions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Findings&lt;/strong&gt;: No evidence of fraudulent activity; transactions deemed non-manipulative.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Legal Precedents&lt;/strong&gt;: Past regulations did not cover the transactions in question; SCN lacks specificity and relies on suspicion.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
